"{\"uid\": \"si.com-olympics-2024-05-01-peacock-increase-subscription-prices-paris-olympics\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"In this story:  Peacock is getting a price hike, as Comcast is going to increase the price of subscriptions for its streaming app by two dollars ahead of the Paris Olympics.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 173, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 52, \"end\": 59, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Comcast\", \"score\": 0.9997373480188175, \"rank\": 0.00026272098541096407, \"text\": \"Comcast\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Comcast\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Comcast\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It will mark the second time the streamer's cost will go up in a year.\", \"from\": 174, \"to\": 244, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It will now cost $7.99 for the version with ads and $13.99 for the ad-free version.\", \"from\": 245, \"to\": 328, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Peacock originally launched in 2020 at just $4.99 per month, and it was $9.99 per month as recently as last spring.\", \"from\": 330, \"to\": 445, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Not long after it was announced that the streamer would carry the first online exclusive NFL playoff game, they raised the prices to $5.99 and $11.99.People complained, but the experiment was deemed a success as 23 million people tuned in to watch.\", \"from\": 446, \"to\": 694, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 535, \"end\": 538, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NFL_on_Fox\", \"score\": 0.998410480619413, \"rank\": 0.001527091352554151, \"text\": \"NFL\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q15416\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NFL_on_Fox\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NFL_on_Fox\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Now they are doing the same thing ahead of the Olympics, which begin on July 26 and run through Aug. 11.\", \"from\": 696, \"to\": 800, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The plan is to make every event available to stream live and on-demand and fans will have the ability to watch up to four events at once.\", \"from\": 801, \"to\": 938, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"NBC has the broadcast rights for the Olympics through 2032.\", \"from\": 939, \"to\": 998, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 939, \"end\": 942, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\", \"score\": 0.9989807326071695, \"rank\": 0.0006742858373711718, \"text\": \"NBC\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Peacock is clearly using sports as the main selling point of their streaming service with NFL, Olympics and even WWE, but it's also their excuse to raise prices.\", \"from\": 1000, \"to\": 1161, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1090, \"end\": 1093, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NFL_on_Fox\", \"score\": 0.998410480619413, \"rank\": 0.001527091352554151, \"text\": \"NFL\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q15416\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NFL_on_Fox\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NFL_on_Fox\"}, {\"begin\": 1113, \"end\": 1116, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WWE\", \"score\": 0.9999999699989535, \"rank\": 2.5570400242713948e-08, \"text\": \"WWE\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WWE\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WWE\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"How else do you expect them to pay for something like thePhiladelphia Eagles' season-opener in Mexico or the Olympic broadcast rights which they currently have through 2032?\", \"from\": 1162, \"to\": 1335, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1257, \"end\": 1263, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mexico\", \"score\": 0.9991123719033521, \"rank\": 0.00043847241249442184, \"text\": \"Mexico\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mexico\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mexico\"}]}, {\"sentence\